OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775952175
OL,3,C87-year-old among 523 people arrested
OL,4,Cat protest against Palestine Action ban
OL,6,FMore than 500 people have been
OL,7,Farrested during a mass protest in
OL,8,Fcentral London against the ban on
OL,9,FPalestine Action, the Metropolitan
OL,10,FPolice said.
OL,12,FThe force said 523 people aged between
OL,13,F18 and 87 were arrested for showing
OL,14,Fsupport for a proscribed organisation
OL,15,Fduring the demonstration at Trafalgar
OL,16,FSquare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
