OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775952175
OL,3,C87-year-old among 523 people arrested
OL,4,Cat protest against Palestine Action ban
OL,6,FThose arrested included Massive Attack
OL,7,Fmusician Robert Del Naja, who sat with
OL,8,Fan "I Support Palestine Action" sign
OL,9,Fand was later carried away by three
OL,10,Fpolice officers.
OL,12,FHundreds of protesters gathered in
OL,13,FTrafalgar Square on Saturday afternoon
OL,14,Fwith signs reading "I oppose genocide.
OL,15,FI support Palestine Action."
OL,17,FProtest group Defend Our Juries said
OL,18,Fthe demonstration, called Everyone
OL,19,FDay, would show the "resistance" to
OL,20,Fthe ban on Palestine Action was
OL,21,F"stronger than ever".
