CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775952175
OL,3,C87-year-old among 523 people arrested
OL,4,Cat protest against Palestine Action ban
OL,6,FMany of the mostly elderly
OL,7,Fdemonstrators sat on camping chairs
OL,8,Fand on the ground as they held up
OL,9,Ftheir placards.
OL,11,FAt the top of the square, near the
OL,12,FNational Gallery, large banners were
OL,13,Fdisplayed reading "Jurors deserve to
OL,14,Fhear the whole truth" and "Israel
OL,15,Fstarves kids".
OL,17,FPolice officers carried people away
OL,18,Ffrom the demonstration as they made
OL,19,Farrests ` including Mr Del Naja, who
OL,20,Fwas filmed being lifted off the ground
OL,21,Fby three police officers.
OL,26,@uD@SOUvD@UO]vD@[OUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
