OL,3,C87-year-old among 523 people arrested
OL,4,Cat protest against Palestine Action ban
OL,6,FIn the footage, a man can be heard
OL,7,Fasking Mr Del Naja: "Can you tell us
OL,8,Fwhy you're being arrested today?"
OL,10,FThe musician appears to reply: "I'm
OL,11,Fbeing unlawfully arrested."
OL,13,FPrior to his arrest, Mr Del Naja told
OL,14,Fthe Press Association he wanted to
OL,15,Fattend the protest despite the
OL,16,Fconsequences a potential arrest could
OL,17,Fhave on his music career.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@aO]rD@`OUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
