PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775952175
OL,3,C87-year-old among 523 people arrested
OL,4,Cat protest against Palestine Action ban
OL,6,F"Being a musician, obviously, there
OL,7,Fwas a lot of trepidation around how we
OL,8,Fmight not be able to travel and get
OL,9,Fvisas," he said.
OL,11,F"But I thought 'this is ridiculous'
OL,12,Fand then the police making that U-turn
OL,13,Fto arrest people again, I thought that
OL,14,Fis even more ridiculous."
OL,16,FHe added: "I think that the actions of
OL,17,FPalestine Action were highly patriotic
OL,18,Fbecause they were pretty much
OL,19,Fprotecting our country from getting
OL,20,Finvolved in serious war crimes, and
OL,21,Fbreaking international law.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]sD@AOUvD@YO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775952175
OL,3,C87-year-old among 523 people arrested
OL,4,Cat protest against Palestine Action ban
OL,6,F"How much more patriotic can you be
OL,7,Fthan that?"
OL,9,FTom Southerden, Amnesty International
OL,10,FUK's law and human rights director,
OL,11,Fsaid: "Today's mass arrests of
OL,12,Fpeaceful protesters in Trafalgar
OL,13,FSquare under UK terrorism law are yet
OL,14,Fanother blow to civil liberties in
OL,15,Fthis country ` and made all the more
OL,16,Foutrageous by the Metropolitan
OL,17,FPolice's own U-turn.
OL,19,F"The High Court ruled in February that
OL,20,Fthe proscription of Palestine Action
OL,21,Fwas unlawful.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@KO]sD@GOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775952175
OL,3,C87-year-old among 523 people arrested
OL,4,Cat protest against Palestine Action ban
OL,6,F"The Met rightly said it would stop
OL,7,Fmaking arrests.
OL,9,F"It has now gone back to its old,
OL,10,Ffailed policy ` mass arrests of people
OL,11,Fholding pieces of card, including
OL,12,Ftoday an elderly woman with walking
OL,13,Fsticks.
OL,15,F"This is not policing. This is the
OL,16,Fstate criminalising dissent."
OL,18,FA Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,19,Fsaid: "We are grateful to all the
OL,20,Fofficers involved for their
OL,21,Fprofessionalism."
